text: Residents of Salisbury Downs, a suburb outside Adelaide, Australia, were stunned to see a huge pig wandering the streets. The pig had escaped from his pen and was eventually returned, according to a local report. https://t.co/diQoFlyJEn https://t.co/bEP6HAYSTn
